we can pass 254 params as arguments in case of non-static methods
we can pass 255 params as arguments in case of static methods
for double and long limit is 127>>param passing

double and long takes 8 bytes
int takes 4 bytes

1 double = 2 int params while passing in methods arguments

Throwable: is the SUPER CLASS of errors and exceptions in JAVA.
Use with try catch block..

Exceptions:
Null Pointer
Arithmetic
Array out of bound


Error:
Out of memory
Unable to load class